<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
      <h1>Welcome to your dashboard</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p>This is where you find everything about your activity</p>

  <p>Your profile :</p>

  <div class="row">
    <div class = "col-xs-12 col-md-4" id = "dashboard-category">
